channel.title: ~~ ProjectCorrupt 317 ~~
channel.description:
[center][img]http://www.projectcorrupt.com/Images/banner.jpg[/img][/center]
[center]!! BETA RELEASE ON 12-23-10 !![/center]
[center]~~ Beta Release ~~ [/center]
[center]In the beta release you will be spawned on "BetaIsland" which is not the complete game but yet a taste of the combat system and skilling system. Anyone who beta tests and post feedback such as suggestions or bugs will be granted access to the exclusive island tele in the full release along with several other items and benefits. Beta release will feature a minigame called BetaBattles which is pretty much a kill till you find the prize game. Not to much but it will be updated and mastered if the feedback shows enjoyment in the game. Not much more to say just check out projectcorrupt.com and keepup to date. Progress so far is as follows below :[/center]
- 70% F2p Complete
- Working F2p Drops
- 100% Donation System
- Special Bosses With New Drops
- Fair Exp Rate (105exp per hit)
- All GodSwords
- Little To No Customs!
- Beautiful Economy
- 50% New Custom Skill Cape Emotes
- 10% Player Owned Areas
- New Minigames
- Normal Shops
- 50% Special Name Icons
- 11 Working Quests
- Working Primitive Clan Chat
- 95% PVP Armor
- 80% PvP Zones
- 100% Working Wilderness
- 75% working doors ALL OVER
- 100% Working Ancients [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/1zyc9cz.jpg[/img]
